  • Reference

    Meta data for Disney Touring Plan Park Data

    parks_metadata_raw.Rd

    A dataset containing daily details on Disney World Parks

    parks_metadata_raw

    Format

    A data frame with 2079 rows and 181 variables:

    date

    Park Day (not actual date stamp of the wait time, since some are after midnight), MM/DD/YYY

    wdw_ticket_season

    Walt Disney World Single Day Price Type, alphanumeric

    dayofweek

    Day of Week, numeric

    dayofyear

    Day of Year (0 to 365), numeric

    weekofyear

    Week of Year (0 to 53), numeric

    monthofyear

    Month of Year (1 to 12), numeric

    year

    Year, numeric

    season

    Seasonal Category (Fall, Winter, Thanksgiving, etc.), alphanumeric

    holidaypx

    Proximity to Holiday (2-directional) (in days), numeric

    holidaym

    Holiday Metric (1 to 5 ranking), numeric

    holidayn

    Name of Holiday, alphanumeric

    holiday

    Day is a Holiday, Boolean

    wdwticketseason

    WDW 1-day ticket season, alphanumeric

    wdwracen

    XXX Event Code, alphanumeric

    wdweventn

    XXX Event Code, alphanumeric

    wdwevent

    WDW Event, Boolean

    wdwrace

    WDW Race, Boolean

    wdwseason

    WDW Season, alphanumeric

    wdwmaxtemp

    WDW Max Temperature, numeric

    wdwmintemp

    WDW Min Temperature, numeric

    wdwmeantemp

    WDW Average Temperature, numeric

    mkeventn

    Magic Kingdom Event Code, alphanumeric

    mkevent

    Magic Kingdom Event, Boolean

    epeventn

    Epcot Event Code, alphanumeric

    epevent

    Epcot Event, Boolean

    hseventn

    Hollywood Studios Event Code, alphanumeric

    hsevent

    Hollywood Studios Event, Boolean

    akeventn

    Animal Kingdom Event Code, alphanumeric

    akevent

    Animal Kingdom Event, Boolean

    holidayj

    Name of Jewish Holiday, alphanumeric

    insession

    Percentage of Schools in Session, numeric

    insession_enrollment

    Percentage of Schools in Session Weighted by Enrollment, numeric

    insession_wdw

    Percentage of Schools in Session WDW markets only, numeric

    insession_dlr

    Percentage of Schools in Session DLR markets only, numeric

    insession_sqrt_wdw

    Percentage of Schools in Session Weighted by Square Root of Distance to WDW, numeric

    insession_sqrt_dlr

    Percentage of Schools in Session Weighted by Square Root of Distance to DLR, numeric

    insession_california

    Percentage of Schools in Session California Only, numeric

    insession_dc

    Percentage of Schools in Session D.C. Only, numeric

    insession_central_fl

    Percentage of Schools in Session Within Central Florida Only, numeric

    insession_drive1_fl

    Percentage of Schools in Session Within Driving Distance to Florida Only, numeric

    insession_drive2_fl

    Percentage of Schools in Session Within Driving Distance to Florida Only, numeric

    insession_drive_ca

    Percentage of Schools in Session Within Driving Distance to California Only, numeric

    insession_florida

    Percentage of Schools in Session Florida Only, numeric

    insession_mardi_gras

    Percentage of Schools in Session Mardi Gras States Only, numeric

    insession_midwest

    Percentage of Schools in Session Midwest Only, numeric

    insession_ny_nj

    Percentage of Schools in Session New York and New Jersey Only, numeric

    insession_ny_nj_pa

    Percentage of Schools in Session New York, New Jersey and Pennsylvania Only, numeric

    insession_new_england

    Percentage of Schools in Session New England Only, numeric

    insession_new_jersey

    Percentage of Schools in Session New Jersey Only, numeric

    insession_nothwest

    Percentage of Schools in Session Northwest Only, numeric

    insession_planes

    Percentage of Schools in Session Planes Only, numeric

    insession_socal

    Percentage of Schools in Session Southern California Only, numeric

    insession_southwest

    Percentage of Schools in Session Southwest Only, numeric
